questions.quote: You actually think that something can happen between Emily and Susan?
Ok. Great. I am so glad that you are here. We're really excited about getting this process started.
Who's so brave, you're so brave, yes you are, you're so brave.
Ohhh! What are you doing to me?! Oh look, I-I... I'm sorry but umm, this-this-this-this is not going to happen.
...and all those dinosaur nick-knacks you have Ross, I thought they might be more at home in the garage.
OK, here we go. Honey, I'm sorry, they were all out of apple pie, someone just got the last piece.
Yeah, I know it sounds crazy, and it's not like me to do something so impulsive, but she's just so perfect, and we have so much in common.
Well, last night you seemed to know your way around the table.
Ross, you have planned out the next 20 years of our lives, we've been dating for six weeks.
Really? Well, if you do, come in the spring. It's just lovely there.
